    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    ActionType
    ActionType is an enum that defines the various actions that can be performed in the application.
    AirTrafficController
    Controller class for managing Air Traffic Control (ATC) related UI and functionality.
    AttendantController
    Controller class for managing flight attendant-related UI and functionality.
    Booking
    Booking is a class that represents a booking made by a passenger.
    BookingDAO
    BookingDAO is a Data Access Object (DAO) class that provides methods to interact with the bookings table in the SQLite database.
    BookingService
    BookingService is a service class that handles booking-related operations.
    BookingServiceTest
     
    BraodcastServiceTest
     
    BroadcastState
    BraodcastState is a singleton class that manages the state of the latest broadcast message.
    CancellationState
    CancellationState is a singleton class that manages the state of the last cancelled passenger.
    ChatMessage
    ChatMessage is a class that represents a chat message in the application.
    ChatMessageDAO
    ChatMessageDAO is a Data Access Object (DAO) class that provides methods to interact with the chat_message table in the SQLite database.
    ChatService
    ChatService is a service class that handles chat-related operations.
    ClientHandler
    The ClientHandler class is responsible for handling communication with a connected client.
    ClientHandlerTest
     
    ClientSocketService
    ClientSocketService is a service class that handles communication with the server using sockets.
    ClientSocketServiceTest
     
    InventoryItem
    InventoryItem is a class that represents an item in the inventory.
    InventoryItemDAO
    InventoryItemDAO is a Data Access Object (DAO) class that provides methods to interact with the inventory_item table in the SQLite database.
    InventoryService
    InventoryService is a service class that handles inventory-related operations.
    Main
    Main class for the JavaFX application.
    MessageEnvelope
    MessageEnvelope is a class that represents a message envelope used in the application.
    Passenger
    Passenger is a class that represents a passenger in the application.
    PassengerController
    Controller class for managing passenger-related UI and functionality.
    PassengerDAO
    PassengerDAO is a Data Access Object (DAO) class that provides methods to interact with the passengers table in the SQLite database.
    PassengerService
    PassengerService is a service class that handles passenger-related operations.
    Photographer
    Photographer is a class that represents a photographer in the application.
    PhotographerController
     
    PhotographerDAO
    PhotographerDAO is a Data Access Object (DAO) class that provides methods to interact with the photographer table in the SQLite database.
    PhotographerDAOTest
     
    PhotographerService
    PhotographerService is a service class that handles photographer-related operations.
    PhotographerServiceTest
     
    PilotController
    Controller class for managing the Pilot role in the application.
    PilotService
    PilotService is a service class that handles pilot-related operations.
    ProtocolHandler
    ProtocolHandler is a class that handles incoming messages and performs actions based on the action type.
    RoleSelectorController
    Controller class for managing the role selection screen in the application.
    RoleWindowLoader
    RoleWindowLoader is responsible for loading the appropriate FXML file based on the user's role.
    Server
    The Server class is responsible for starting the server and listening for incoming client connections.
    SpacewalkSlot
    SpacewalkSlot is a class that represents a spacewalk slot in the application.
    SpacewalkSlotDAO
    SpacewalkSlotDAO is a Data Access Object (DAO) class that provides methods to interact with the spacewalk_slots table in the SQLite database.
    SQLiteConnector
    SQLiteConnector is a utility class that provides a method to establish a connection to the SQLite database.
    StartApp
    This is the main entry point for the application.
    SurveyState
    SurveyState is a singleton class that manages the state of the survey trigger.
    UserRole
    UserRole is an enumeration that represents the different roles a user can have in the application.
